                },
                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>The nosferatu can cast @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Dominate] at will as a divine innate spell. Casting it requires staring into the target's eyes, giving the spell the visual trait. The save DC uses a high DC for the nosferatu's level, and a creature that succeeds is temporarily immune to that nosferatu's Dominate for 24 hours. Fully destroying the nosferatu ends the domination, but merely reducing the nosferatu to 0 HP is insufficient to break the spell.</p>"
