        {
            "_id": "h9mHi6QSWZbtncRc",
            "folder": "Pycs65tqRMBiiARd",
            "img": "systems/pf2e/icons/actions/Passive.webp",
            "name": "Plague of Ancients",
            "sort": 1400000,
            "system": {
                "actionType": {
                    "value": "passive"
                },
                "actions": {
                    "value": null
                },
                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p><strong>Saving Throw</strong> @Check[fortitude|dc:29]</p><hr /><p><strong>Onset</strong> 1 day</p>\n<p><strong>Stage 1</strong> @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Drained]{Drained 1} (1 day)</p>\n<p><strong>Stage 2</strong> @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Drained]{Drained 2} and @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Enfeebled]{Enfeebled 2} (1 day)</p>\n<p><strong>Stage 3</strong> @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Doomed]{Doomed 1}, @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Drained]{Drained 3}, and @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Enfeebled]{Enfeebled 3} (1 day)</p>\n<p><strong>Stage 4</strong> @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Doomed]{Doomed 2}, drained 3, and enfeebled 3 (1 day)</p>\n<p><strong>Stage 5</strong> @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Unconscious] (1 day)</p>\n<p><strong>Stage 6</strong> death</p>"
